metadata.name: CHAINED
metadata.description:
They chained me, my body, my mind, my soul, they chained me, but it's enough, I will release myself, I will save myself, I will release my chained mind from this soulless imaginary prison.

Hand drew with pencil, graphite, charcoal, Conte, brush, and eraser on heavy cardboard.

Physical drawing size: 11.5 x 18 cm

Scanned file size: 2656 x 4227 pixels
